Osborne Says EU Won’t Discriminate on Derivatives Clearing

-- B y   G o n z a l o   V i n a
-- 
2011-10-04T15:13:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/osborne-says-eu-won-t-discriminate-on-derivatives-clearing.html
U.K. Chancellor of the Exchequer
 George Osborne  said that European Union finance ministers have
agreed to a deal that will protect Britain’s role in the
clearing of derivatives. He spoke to reporters in Luxembourg
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
